1
00:01:37,320 --> 00:01:38,600
The Divine Machine Battalion of our Great Ming

2
00:01:38,840 --> 00:01:40,520
bears the heavy responsibility of guarding the capital

3
00:01:40,920 --> 00:01:42,600
and preparing for campaigns abroad.

4
00:01:43,800 --> 00:01:46,600
You have managed the Divine Machine Battalion for over three years.

5
00:01:48,960 --> 00:01:50,520
Regarding the position of Minister of War,

6
00:01:51,560 --> 00:01:54,040
I intend to recommend you to His Majesty.

7
00:01:54,720 --> 00:01:57,640
What are your thoughts on this?

8
00:01:58,280 --> 00:01:59,440
I am overwhelmed with trepidation.

9
00:01:59,600 --> 00:02:00,680
The position of Minister of War

10
00:02:00,920 --> 00:02:02,600
has long been coveted by the Eastern Depot.

11
00:02:02,800 --> 00:02:03,520
I fear that...

12
00:02:03,720 --> 00:02:05,400
Last night, Li Chenyang

13
00:02:05,480 --> 00:02:06,720
was hijacked at the execution ground,

14
00:02:07,080 --> 00:02:09,640
and Feng Hai of the Eastern Depot was assassinated.

15
00:02:10,200 --> 00:02:11,920
You must have heard about it.

16
00:02:13,240 --> 00:02:14,320
If I can take on this great responsibility,

17
00:02:14,640 --> 00:02:15,960
I will certainly know my place

18
00:02:16,360 --> 00:02:18,160
and serve the Eunuch Lord with my life.

19
00:02:18,680 --> 00:02:19,920
Do you know why His Majesty

20
00:02:20,160 --> 00:02:21,560
keeps the Divine Machine Battalion's

21
00:02:21,800 --> 00:02:23,680
former General Lin Feng's

22
00:02:23,680 --> 00:02:25,000
sword

23
00:02:25,440 --> 00:02:27,240
and musket enshrined here?

24
00:02:27,280 --> 00:02:29,400
Three years ago, General Lin Feng

25
00:02:29,760 --> 00:02:31,720
led three hundred soldiers of the Divine Machine Battalion

26
00:02:31,840 --> 00:02:33,200
to set an ambush in the canyon,

27
00:02:33,560 --> 00:02:35,520
luring ten thousand Oirat cavalry to approach.

28
00:02:35,880 --> 00:02:37,200
They resisted until the very last moment,

29
00:02:37,880 --> 00:02:39,640
allowing Eunuch Lord Wang to lead reinforcements in time

30
00:02:39,640 --> 00:02:40,600
to strike the Oirat

31
00:02:40,720 --> 00:02:41,920
and win a great victory.

32
00:02:42,320 --> 00:02:45,000
General Lin and the three hundred soldiers died in glory.

33
00:02:45,200 --> 00:02:47,880
Ming soldiers must take this as an example.

34
00:02:53,200 --> 00:02:54,360
A small gift.

35
00:02:55,320 --> 00:02:56,680
Please accept it, General.

36
00:02:57,200 --> 00:02:58,200
Thank you, Eunuch Lord Wang.

37
00:02:59,080 --> 00:03:01,680
This is the weapon of a guard who followed me for years.

38
00:03:02,200 --> 00:03:04,040
I remember his name was Ya.

39
00:03:04,320 --> 00:03:06,880
He served the Eastern Depot Eunuch Lord Shang Hua.

40
00:03:07,480 --> 00:03:08,560
Until five years ago,

41
00:03:08,600 --> 00:03:10,400
when I became the Eunuch Lord of the Western Depot

42
00:03:10,720 --> 00:03:12,320
and took control of all Ming guards.

43
00:03:12,320 --> 00:03:13,480
He came to serve me.

44
00:03:13,720 --> 00:03:15,200
I am not a narrow-minded person.

45
00:03:15,640 --> 00:03:16,560
But he...

46
00:03:16,680 --> 00:03:18,600
tried to kill me with this dagger.

47
00:03:19,360 --> 00:03:20,200
In the end,

48
00:03:20,800 --> 00:03:22,560
he became a ghost under the blade.

49
00:03:22,560 --> 00:03:24,800
I will not fail Eunuch Lord Wang's kindness.

50
00:03:27,560 --> 00:03:28,840
Keep everything hidden in your heart,

51
00:03:29,680 --> 00:03:31,200
and show nothing on your face.

52
00:03:31,840 --> 00:03:33,520
In this imperial capital,

53
00:03:34,080 --> 00:03:36,080
I see all kinds of guards every day.

54
00:03:36,080 --> 00:03:37,360
I keep thinking,

55
00:03:37,920 --> 00:03:40,040
why don't they kill me right now?

56
00:03:40,280 --> 00:03:42,720
If I were a Divine Machine Battalion soldier or a guard,

57
00:03:43,040 --> 00:03:44,400
I would shoot and kill me.

58
00:03:44,960 --> 00:03:45,560
Right now.

59
00:03:45,560 --> 00:03:46,520
At this very moment.

60
00:03:46,720 --> 00:03:48,040
But you have never done so.

61
00:03:48,160 --> 00:03:48,640
Why?

62
00:03:48,640 --> 00:03:49,600
I dare not.

63
00:03:55,600 --> 00:03:56,880
Think carefully.

64
00:03:58,200 --> 00:04:00,440
Who exactly are you and I sacrificing our lives for?

65
00:04:02,000 --> 00:04:03,480
Do not speculate wildly.

66
00:04:20,280 --> 00:04:22,200
Rebels infiltrated Linggu Temple.

67
00:04:22,360 --> 00:04:23,720
Such an absurd thing,

68
00:04:23,720 --> 00:04:24,160
do you believe it?

69
00:04:24,480 --> 00:04:25,560
I'd rather believe

70
00:04:25,680 --> 00:04:27,560
that the Snow Woman Dou E has appeared,

71
00:04:27,680 --> 00:04:29,320
and Li Chenyang learned sorcery.

72
00:04:29,640 --> 00:04:31,240
I heard that those who died at Linggu Temple

73
00:04:31,240 --> 00:04:32,880
were all Eastern Depot sleeper agents.

74
00:04:33,160 --> 00:04:34,720
The Western Depot suffered again.

75
00:04:35,160 --> 00:04:36,040
Let me tell you,

76
00:04:36,080 --> 00:04:38,320
tonight, many high officials and nobles

77
00:04:38,360 --> 00:04:39,240
in luxury carriages

78
00:04:39,360 --> 00:04:40,520
went towards the palace.

79
00:04:41,040 --> 00:04:42,520
Is something big going to happen?

80
00:04:43,160 --> 00:04:44,600
I heard it is to pay respects

81
00:04:44,600 --> 00:04:46,920
at the prayer lantern festival held by Master Konghui.

82
00:04:47,160 --> 00:04:47,840
Inviting

83
00:04:48,000 --> 00:04:50,240
officials of the fourth rank and above with their families.

84
00:04:50,440 --> 00:04:52,160
Consort Wan is hosting it personally.

85
00:04:59,400 --> 00:04:59,800
My Lord.

86
00:05:03,000 --> 00:05:04,280
Remember what I instructed.

87
00:05:05,360 --> 00:05:07,240
When the palace lantern rises, all is well.

88
00:05:19,320 --> 00:05:20,000
Lord Pei, Lord Zhang.

89
00:05:20,160 --> 00:05:20,640
Excuse me.

90
00:05:21,480 --> 00:05:22,760
For today's prayer lantern festival in the palace,

91
00:05:22,880 --> 00:05:24,520
no one is allowed to carry weapons into the palace.

92
00:05:25,040 --> 00:05:25,960
Accompanying guards and coachmen

93
00:05:25,960 --> 00:05:26,880
must wait outside the palace.

94
00:05:27,120 --> 00:05:27,480
Very well.

95
00:05:28,880 --> 00:05:29,760
You return to the Grand Court of Justice first.

96
00:05:30,200 --> 00:05:31,000
No need to wait here.

97
00:05:31,040 --> 00:05:31,760
Yes, my Lord.

98
00:05:42,560 --> 00:05:43,640
No matter how audacious they are,

99
00:05:43,920 --> 00:05:44,840
they wouldn't dare trespass

100
00:05:44,840 --> 00:05:46,080
into the heavily guarded Inner Court.

101
00:05:46,440 --> 00:05:47,560
If you intend to shield them,

102
00:05:48,600 --> 00:05:50,320
you should see the situation clearly tonight.

103
00:05:51,280 --> 00:05:52,600
The one from the Western Depot

104
00:05:53,960 --> 00:05:55,600
is bound to make a move tonight.

105
00:05:58,320 --> 00:06:00,360
If Zhang Yi brings Tang Xi into the palace,

106
00:06:00,720 --> 00:06:01,880
wouldn't it be a desperate struggle?

107
00:06:06,520 --> 00:06:07,520
Embroidered Uniform Guard, listen up.

108
00:06:07,600 --> 00:06:08,200
Here.

109
00:06:09,600 --> 00:06:11,880
Strictly check the identities of maids and eunuchs at the lantern festival.

110
00:06:12,200 --> 00:06:13,840
Prevent Tang Xi and his kind from sneaking in.

111
00:06:14,360 --> 00:06:15,280
If discovered,

112
00:06:15,840 --> 00:06:17,320
bring them to me immediately.

113
00:06:18,080 --> 00:06:18,680
Yes, sir.

114
00:06:20,480 --> 00:06:22,320
Rather than falling into the Western Depot's hands,

115
00:06:23,240 --> 00:06:24,520
it is better to strike first.

116
00:06:25,400 --> 00:06:27,440
Zhang Yi, do not do anything foolish.

117
00:06:32,800 --> 00:06:34,240
Shuimo, Danqing.

118
00:06:34,600 --> 00:06:35,600
Why have you returned?

119
00:06:36,040 --> 00:06:37,000
Shouldn't you be at the palace gate

120
00:06:37,000 --> 00:06:38,680
waiting for Lord Pei and Vice Minister Zhang?

121
00:06:39,040 --> 00:06:39,760
Our master

122
00:06:39,760 --> 00:06:41,280
never cares for such tedious formalities.

123
00:06:41,800 --> 00:06:43,000
Wait until the prayer lanterns

124
00:06:43,000 --> 00:06:44,080
rise within the palace tonight.

125
00:06:44,360 --> 00:06:44,800
Danqing.

126
00:06:45,240 --> 00:06:46,480
There are still many files to organize.

127
00:06:47,320 --> 00:06:48,200
Shuimo, wait for me.

128
00:06:48,280 --> 00:06:48,760
You talk too much.

129
00:06:50,080 --> 00:06:51,800
Only by acting as usual will no suspicion arise.

130
00:06:59,680 --> 00:07:00,240
Reporting, my lord.

131
00:07:00,880 --> 00:07:02,720
We have safely escorted Vice Minister Zhang

132
00:07:03,040 --> 00:07:04,000
into the palace for the lantern festival.

133
00:07:04,720 --> 00:07:05,240
From here on,

134
00:07:06,000 --> 00:07:06,760
it all depends on

135
00:07:06,760 --> 00:07:07,920
the two of them and their fate.

136
00:07:08,400 --> 00:07:09,200
If you ask me,

137
00:07:09,520 --> 00:07:10,680
Lord Zhang this time is like

138
00:07:10,680 --> 00:07:12,280
Wu Dalang marrying a wife in *Water Margin*.

139
00:07:12,680 --> 00:07:13,440
What does that mean?

140
00:07:13,600 --> 00:07:14,720
It bodes ill rather than well.

141
00:07:16,600 --> 00:07:18,000
I told you to read *Water Margin*.

142
00:07:18,480 --> 00:07:19,560
You only read useless things.

143
00:07:20,000 --> 00:07:21,280
That storyteller stuff...

144
00:07:23,800 --> 00:07:24,960
Gu Gong Dan Fu,

145
00:07:26,040 --> 00:07:27,160
came galloping at dawn,

146
00:07:27,760 --> 00:07:28,960
along the western riverbanks,

147
00:07:30,560 --> 00:07:31,720
arriving at the foot of Mount Qi.

148
00:07:34,040 --> 00:07:35,680
What I can do for Zhang Yi

149
00:07:35,920 --> 00:07:37,440
ends here.

150
00:07:37,880 --> 00:07:40,400
I hope the prayer lanterns in the palace tonight

151
00:07:40,880 --> 00:07:42,160
rise as usual.

152
00:07:52,680 --> 00:07:53,440
You infiltrate the Inner Palace.

153
00:07:53,440 --> 00:07:54,280
You must be extra careful.

154
00:07:54,760 --> 00:07:55,280
Find them

155
00:07:55,440 --> 00:07:56,280
and regroup as soon as possible.

156
00:07:57,560 --> 00:07:58,360
I await your good news.

157
00:07:58,720 --> 00:07:59,720
Do not be impatient.

158
00:08:21,360 --> 00:08:22,200
Your Highness.

159
00:08:28,640 --> 00:08:29,480
Consort Wan.

160
00:08:29,760 --> 00:08:31,360
Consort Xian is here to pay her respects.

161
00:08:34,080 --> 00:08:35,720
No one stays in favor forever,

162
00:08:35,960 --> 00:08:37,240
just as no flower blooms for a hundred days.

163
00:08:38,080 --> 00:08:39,000
She certainly chooses to come

164
00:08:39,000 --> 00:08:40,440
when one is out of favor and luck.

165
00:08:58,320 --> 00:09:00,120
Consort Xian pays her respects to the Noble Consort.

166
00:09:00,280 --> 00:09:02,400
May the Noble Consort enjoy ten thousand blessings.

167
00:09:07,800 --> 00:09:10,200
You are usually busy attending to the Empress, Sister.

168
00:09:10,480 --> 00:09:11,720
How did you find time today?

169
00:09:11,880 --> 00:09:12,960
To come to my palace...

170
00:09:12,960 --> 00:09:13,800
...and visit this old woman?

171
00:09:14,480 --> 00:09:15,280
Perhaps...

172
00:09:15,440 --> 00:09:16,640
...you have run into some trouble?

173
00:09:17,920 --> 00:09:18,960
You jest, Sister.

174
00:09:19,480 --> 00:09:20,720
The difficulties I encounter...

175
00:09:20,800 --> 00:09:23,000
...are but a lonely courtyard where spring fades late.

176
00:09:23,760 --> 00:09:25,600
Over the years, I have grown accustomed to it.

177
00:09:26,120 --> 00:09:26,920
Unlike you, Sister.

178
00:09:27,200 --> 00:09:28,320
You have obtained what every woman...

179
00:09:28,320 --> 00:09:29,960
...in this world desires most.

180
00:09:30,280 --> 00:09:31,640
It is truly enviable.

181
00:09:31,720 --> 00:09:32,680
It is rare indeed...

182
00:09:32,800 --> 00:09:33,960
...to hear you speak such dispirited words.

183
00:09:34,200 --> 00:09:35,640
They are clearly the honest truth.

184
00:09:36,240 --> 00:09:37,640
At my age...

185
00:09:37,800 --> 00:09:39,400
...to still hope for a child...

186
00:09:39,560 --> 00:09:40,920
...is the true joke of the palace.

187
00:09:43,480 --> 00:09:44,040
Bring it here.

188
00:09:48,000 --> 00:09:49,520
His Majesty specially ordered the Sewing Bureau...

189
00:09:49,640 --> 00:09:52,200
...to tailor a ritual prayer dress for you, Sister.

190
00:09:52,600 --> 00:09:53,760
The Empress has already inspected it...

191
00:09:54,000 --> 00:09:54,960
...and specially ordered me to deliver it...

192
00:09:55,000 --> 00:09:56,240
...and assist you in dressing up.

193
00:10:00,240 --> 00:10:00,840
Insolence!

194
00:10:01,960 --> 00:10:03,200
How does the Sewing Bureau conduct its business?

195
00:10:03,520 --> 00:10:04,800
Do they think this phoenix pattern...

196
00:10:04,840 --> 00:10:06,320
...is something I am permitted to wear?

197
00:10:06,600 --> 00:10:07,680
Please quell your anger, Noble Consort.

198
00:10:07,960 --> 00:10:10,120
The pattern on this dress was drawn by His Majesty himself.

199
00:10:10,400 --> 00:10:12,720
The Sewing Bureau worked seven nights to rush it.

200
00:10:12,960 --> 00:10:14,320
It was not us acting on our own authority.

201
00:10:14,720 --> 00:10:16,800
Otherwise, it would not have been sent to the Empress...

202
00:10:16,800 --> 00:10:18,160
...for review before being brought here.

203
00:10:18,440 --> 00:10:20,280
The moon on the sea is the moon in the sky.

204
00:10:20,680 --> 00:10:22,440
The one before your eyes is the one in his heart.

205
00:10:22,880 --> 00:10:25,440
Most women in the harem lose favor as beauty fades.

206
00:10:25,720 --> 00:10:28,040
Their honor and disgrace are tied to their family's favor.

207
00:10:28,320 --> 00:10:29,680
You, Sister, are like a phoenix spreading its wings.

208
00:10:29,840 --> 00:10:32,000
You have held favor in the harem for over eighteen years.

209
00:10:32,240 --> 00:10:34,080
Now you even have the Little Prince by your side.

210
00:10:34,880 --> 00:10:36,560
Do you still not understand...

211
00:10:36,800 --> 00:10:38,720
...the weight you hold in His Majesty's heart?

212
00:10:40,400 --> 00:10:41,680
So what if I understand?

213
00:10:42,440 --> 00:10:43,240
Nowadays...

214
00:10:43,800 --> 00:10:45,200
...no matter how much I dress up...

215
00:10:45,520 --> 00:10:47,880
...I cannot withstand the ravages of time.

216
00:10:49,120 --> 00:10:52,120
All women in the world desire quiet and peaceful years...

217
00:10:52,520 --> 00:10:53,680
...and to halt the fleeting prime of youth.

218
00:10:54,160 --> 00:10:55,440
But a woman's life...

219
00:10:55,760 --> 00:10:57,720
...is like a spring flower budding...

220
00:10:58,120 --> 00:11:00,000
...blooming with the brilliance of summer flowers...

221
00:11:00,160 --> 00:11:02,440
...mature and bright like autumn leaves...

222
00:11:02,800 --> 00:11:04,800
...and pure and imposing like winter snow.

223
00:11:05,520 --> 00:11:06,520
Everything one experiences...

224
00:11:07,080 --> 00:11:08,280
...is a gift.

225
00:11:40,800 --> 00:11:42,280
Compared to the newcomers in the palace...

226
00:11:42,520 --> 00:11:43,800
...amidst their natural charm...

227
00:11:44,000 --> 00:11:45,760
...you possess more steadiness and dignity.

228
00:11:46,720 --> 00:11:48,800
Rather than worrying about a fading reflection...

229
00:11:49,000 --> 00:11:51,240
...it is better to ensure one does not lose one's heart.

230
00:11:52,520 --> 00:11:54,280
Thank you for your trouble today, Sister.

231
00:11:55,080 --> 00:11:57,400
Then I shall go report back to the Empress.

232
00:11:57,840 --> 00:11:59,480
May the Noble Consort's prayers today...

233
00:11:59,480 --> 00:12:00,520
...go smoothly.

234
00:12:17,320 --> 00:12:18,520
Did you get the key?

235
00:12:18,960 --> 00:12:19,640
I got it.

236
00:12:22,640 --> 00:12:23,480
Halt, you servants ahead!

237
00:12:24,000 --> 00:12:25,040
The Prayer Lantern Festival is about to begin.

238
00:12:25,240 --> 00:12:26,600
We are strictly checking everyone's identity.

239
00:12:27,200 --> 00:12:27,840
Reporting to my lord...

240
00:12:28,160 --> 00:12:28,680
I...

241
00:12:28,760 --> 00:12:29,600
How dare you!

242
00:12:32,480 --> 00:12:34,400
You dare to stop Consort Xian?

243
00:12:35,480 --> 00:12:37,760
You mindless fools!

244
00:12:39,560 --> 00:12:41,440
The Prayer Lantern Festival is about to begin.

245
00:12:42,000 --> 00:12:43,160
Consort Xian...

246
00:12:43,240 --> 00:12:46,680
...must accompany the Empress's carriage.

247
00:12:48,640 --> 00:12:50,280
If the hour is missed...

248
00:12:50,360 --> 00:12:51,320
...and blame is assigned...

249
00:12:52,440 --> 00:12:55,760
...how many heads do you have to lose?

250
00:12:58,200 --> 00:12:59,240
The Eunuch is right to remind us.

251
00:12:59,480 --> 00:13:00,360
We were rash.

252
00:13:01,200 --> 00:13:02,360
Please forgive us, Consort Xian.

253
00:13:03,200 --> 00:13:04,000
Consort Xian...

254
00:13:05,000 --> 00:13:05,440
Please.

255
00:13:21,080 --> 00:13:22,840
Greetings, Superintendent of the Eastern Depot.

256
00:13:22,960 --> 00:13:24,080
Deputy Commander of the Embroidered Uniform Guard.

257
00:13:24,640 --> 00:13:26,280
I wonder why your Excellencies have visited the Grand Court of Justice.

258
00:13:26,640 --> 00:13:27,440
What business brings you here?

259
00:13:27,600 --> 00:13:28,520
We received information.

260
00:13:28,720 --> 00:13:30,560
Suspecting that Minister Pei Yuandong of the Grand Court...

261
00:13:30,560 --> 00:13:31,520
...and Lord Zhang Yi...

262
00:13:31,720 --> 00:13:32,760
...will be harmed by villains.

263
00:13:33,200 --> 00:13:34,800
So we came specifically to investigate.

264
00:13:36,200 --> 00:13:37,480
Superintendent, you worry too much.

265
00:13:37,680 --> 00:13:38,840
Lord Pei and Lord Zhang...

266
00:13:38,840 --> 00:13:40,240
...were personally escorted by us into the palace...

267
00:13:40,520 --> 00:13:42,080
...to attend Consort Wan's prayer lantern festival.

268
00:13:42,360 --> 00:13:43,800
How could they be harmed at the Grand Court?

269
00:13:43,880 --> 00:13:44,840
Ignorant fool.

270
00:13:45,560 --> 00:13:46,720
A mere Grand Court of Justice...

271
00:13:46,960 --> 00:13:48,760
...what right does it have to question our words?

272
00:13:49,480 --> 00:13:50,000
Men!

273
00:13:50,360 --> 00:13:51,520
Search the Grand Court from top to bottom.

274
00:13:51,800 --> 00:13:52,880
Leave no stone unturned.

275
00:14:15,200 --> 00:14:16,600
The Li Chenyang case is settled.

276
00:14:16,880 --> 00:14:18,920
Vice Minister Zhang contributed greatly and was rewarded by His Majesty.

277
00:14:19,160 --> 00:14:20,520
You look radiant right now.

278
00:14:20,800 --> 00:14:23,040
Doesn't it feel like spring is in the air?

279
00:14:23,160 --> 00:14:25,320
Could it be that good things are happening one after another?

280
00:14:25,400 --> 00:14:27,720
Is there some good news you want to announce to us?

281
00:14:28,400 --> 00:14:29,480
Minister Wang, you are teasing me.

282
00:14:30,440 --> 00:14:32,040
That the Grand Court could solve the case and escape trouble...

283
00:14:32,040 --> 00:14:33,040
...is already a great fortune.

284
00:14:33,800 --> 00:14:34,640
If...

285
00:14:35,360 --> 00:14:37,160
...Li Chenyang had been handled by the Ministry of Justice...

286
00:14:37,760 --> 00:14:38,680
Minister Wang...

287
00:14:38,880 --> 00:14:40,400
...you might not have fared any better than I did.

288
00:14:43,000 --> 00:14:43,720
Lord Zhang.

289
00:14:43,920 --> 00:14:45,560
Now you are making things up out of nothing.

290
00:14:45,920 --> 00:14:46,720
That Li Chenyang...

291
00:14:46,720 --> 00:14:48,520
...was supposed to be the Grand Court's responsibility.

292
00:14:48,720 --> 00:14:50,000
What does it have to do with us?

293
00:14:50,560 --> 00:14:51,160
Minister Yuan.

294
00:14:51,280 --> 00:14:52,400
You be the judge.

295
00:14:55,040 --> 00:14:55,800
It is quite good.

296
00:14:56,200 --> 00:14:56,560
No...

297
00:14:57,000 --> 00:14:58,520
What kind of talk is that?

298
00:14:59,760 --> 00:15:00,800
Minister Wang.

299
00:15:01,120 --> 00:15:02,920
The dust has settled on this matter.

300
00:15:03,320 --> 00:15:05,400
The outcome was decided by His Majesty.

301
00:15:05,800 --> 00:15:07,800
Naturally, it is exceptionally good.

302
00:15:10,200 --> 00:15:11,520
It seems Minister Yuan...

303
00:15:11,760 --> 00:15:13,920
...is truly an expert at judging matters.

304
00:15:14,320 --> 00:15:16,120
No wonder your family is harmonious.

305
00:15:16,360 --> 00:15:17,760
With a kind mother and filial son.

306
00:15:20,320 --> 00:15:21,040
You are envious?

307
00:15:21,400 --> 00:15:22,760
Then go ahead.

308
00:15:24,200 --> 00:15:26,320
My Yuan Ling is not yet married.

309
00:15:26,560 --> 00:15:28,920
If Minister Wang shows such favor...

310
00:15:30,040 --> 00:15:32,200
...it is us who are unworthy of the honor.

311
00:15:37,400 --> 00:15:39,560
Greetings, Eunuch Lord Shang.

312
00:15:40,720 --> 00:15:41,800
Everyone, no need for formalities.

313
00:15:41,960 --> 00:15:43,400
Continue, please continue.

314
00:15:44,920 --> 00:15:45,880
Vice Minister Zhang.

315
00:15:46,280 --> 00:15:47,720
I just looked around.

316
00:15:47,960 --> 00:15:49,600
I did not see Minister Pei of the Grand Court.

317
00:15:50,040 --> 00:15:51,360
I wonder where Lord Pei has gone.

318
00:15:54,000 --> 00:15:55,760
When Lord Pei first arrived...

319
00:15:56,120 --> 00:15:57,200
...he suddenly felt unwell.

320
00:15:57,960 --> 00:15:58,600
At this moment...

321
00:16:00,000 --> 00:16:01,080
...he is likely relieving himself.

322
00:16:02,280 --> 00:16:03,320
Vice Minister Zhang.

323
00:16:04,840 --> 00:16:06,000
Nature calls.

324
00:16:06,400 --> 00:16:07,320
If it is urgent...

325
00:16:07,400 --> 00:16:08,480
...how can he be so slow?

326
00:16:08,920 --> 00:16:10,440
I was merely delayed by something.

327
00:16:10,440 --> 00:16:11,680
Arriving late.

328
00:16:12,200 --> 00:16:14,000
Stop talking nonsense here.

329
00:16:14,160 --> 00:16:15,200
And demeaning yourself.

330
00:16:18,840 --> 00:16:19,280
My Lord.

331
00:16:21,880 --> 00:16:22,920
Lord Pei.

332
00:16:23,280 --> 00:16:24,520
What was it that delayed you?

333
00:16:24,640 --> 00:16:27,520
I went across to check on my second wife.

334
00:16:28,440 --> 00:16:30,360
It is my wife's first time attending a palace banquet.

335
00:16:30,720 --> 00:16:32,280
She is inevitably a bit nervous.

336
00:16:33,080 --> 00:16:34,760
I just went to give her a few words of advice.

337
00:16:35,080 --> 00:16:36,120
To avoid any mistakes.

338
00:16:38,720 --> 00:16:39,960
I see, I see.

339
00:16:42,200 --> 00:16:43,200
Everyone, please continue.

340
00:17:01,840 --> 00:17:02,880
I miscalculated.

341
00:17:03,400 --> 00:17:05,200
I didn't expect Zhang Yi to do the exact opposite.

342
00:17:05,560 --> 00:17:06,880
Letting them so boldly impersonate

343
00:17:06,880 --> 00:17:08,680
the families of court officials to sneak into the palace.

344
00:17:09,760 --> 00:17:10,760
Exposing them now

345
00:17:11,240 --> 00:17:12,720
would undoubtedly be letting them walk right into

346
00:17:12,720 --> 00:17:14,480
the Western Depot's dragnet.

347
00:17:15,240 --> 00:17:16,120
Lord Zhang.

348
00:17:17,760 --> 00:17:18,920
I certainly don't recall

349
00:17:19,640 --> 00:17:21,200
that Lord Pei's second wife

350
00:17:21,760 --> 00:17:22,680
is Yuan Ran.

351
00:17:22,880 --> 00:17:23,840
She is as of today.

352
00:17:24,280 --> 00:17:25,240
In that case,

353
00:17:25,880 --> 00:17:27,200
Tang Xi has also snuck in among the female relatives.

354
00:17:27,200 --> 00:17:28,080
What do you mean "snuck in"?

355
00:17:29,360 --> 00:17:30,360
Those over there are all

356
00:17:30,360 --> 00:17:31,360
respectable female relatives.

357
00:17:31,760 --> 00:17:32,440
Watch your mouth.

358
00:17:33,560 --> 00:17:34,520
For what purpose

359
00:17:35,040 --> 00:17:36,560
do you risk your lives to sneak into the palace?

360
00:17:37,880 --> 00:17:39,320
Naturally, to pray for the common people.

361
00:17:40,240 --> 00:17:41,440
Wishing for peace and prosperity.

362
00:17:45,080 --> 00:17:46,640
This lady looks unfamiliar.

363
00:17:46,760 --> 00:17:48,520
May I ask which official's family you belong to?

364
00:17:49,720 --> 00:17:51,400
It is Lord Pei Yuandong's family.

365
00:17:51,400 --> 00:17:52,880
His newly wedded second wife.

366
00:17:54,880 --> 00:17:55,720
Ah, Lord Pei.

367
00:17:56,200 --> 00:17:57,840
Lord Pei certainly has it tough.

368
00:17:59,160 --> 00:18:00,040
I have it tough too.

369
00:18:01,200 --> 00:18:02,840
Lady Pei, please wait a moment longer.

370
00:18:03,600 --> 00:18:05,160
Once the prayer ceremony ends,

371
00:18:05,600 --> 00:18:07,080
we can leave the palace.

372
00:18:08,560 --> 00:18:09,960
Thank you, Auntie.

373
00:18:14,640 --> 00:18:17,200
Consort Wan arrives!

374
00:18:19,520 --> 00:18:23,000
Your Highness, long live, long live, long live!

375
00:18:26,720 --> 00:18:28,400
Consort Wan has changed her attire.

376
00:18:28,680 --> 00:18:30,240
She must have discovered the key is lost.

377
00:18:40,560 --> 00:18:42,240
If I am not mistaken,

378
00:18:42,920 --> 00:18:44,520
the master of ceremonies leading the team

379
00:18:44,520 --> 00:18:47,120
appears to be Eunuch Lord Wang of the Western Depot.

380
00:18:49,320 --> 00:18:50,280
Have you gentlemen received

381
00:18:50,720 --> 00:18:52,240
His Majesty's edict pardoning Eunuch Lord Wang?

382
00:18:52,760 --> 00:18:54,440
That depends on the Emperor's will.

383
00:18:54,960 --> 00:18:57,880
After all, Eunuch Lord Wang is not under our jurisdiction.

384
00:19:10,640 --> 00:19:11,640
My lords,

385
00:19:12,880 --> 00:19:15,000
as the Prayer Lantern Festival begins,

386
00:19:15,680 --> 00:19:17,080
in Consort Wan's palace,

387
00:19:17,400 --> 00:19:19,320
an item gifted by His Majesty has gone missing.

388
00:19:20,000 --> 00:19:20,960
This is a grave matter.

389
00:19:22,360 --> 00:19:24,720
To avoid damaging your reputations,

390
00:19:25,440 --> 00:19:27,720
we will now conduct a full search.

391
00:19:32,240 --> 00:19:33,120
My lord, pardon the offense.

392
00:19:33,120 --> 00:19:33,800
Pardon the offense, my lord.

393
00:19:35,120 --> 00:19:35,840
Routine procedure.

394
00:19:38,680 --> 00:19:39,880
Lord Wang, pardon the offense.

395
00:19:40,280 --> 00:19:41,160
Pardon the offense, Madam.

396
00:19:41,280 --> 00:19:42,040
Forgive me, my lord.

397
00:19:44,080 --> 00:19:44,560
Pardon me.

398
00:19:46,120 --> 00:19:46,760
My lord.

399
00:19:47,760 --> 00:19:48,320
My lord.

400
00:19:52,360 --> 00:19:53,080
Pardon me.

401
00:20:00,560 --> 00:20:01,560
Pardon me, Madam.

402
00:20:03,520 --> 00:20:04,200
Reporting, my lord.

403
00:20:04,320 --> 00:20:05,040
We found nothing.

404
00:20:06,840 --> 00:20:07,640
Your Highness,

405
00:20:07,840 --> 00:20:09,560
the female guests do not have your key.

406
00:20:17,120 --> 00:20:19,280
After we successfully take the key from Consort Wan,

407
00:20:19,320 --> 00:20:21,240
Consort Wan will surely discover it is missing.

408
00:20:21,600 --> 00:20:23,560
Then the entire palace will be on lockdown.

409
00:20:23,760 --> 00:20:25,080
How will we evade the search

410
00:20:25,080 --> 00:20:26,160
and leave the palace?

411
00:20:26,760 --> 00:20:27,440
Disguise.

412
00:20:28,560 --> 00:20:29,880
No one is more skilled at

413
00:20:29,880 --> 00:20:31,400
misdirection and substitution than you.

414
00:20:32,640 --> 00:20:34,440
Consort Wan wears the key on her person,

415
00:20:34,440 --> 00:20:36,560
which means it is an exquisitely made key.

416
00:20:36,760 --> 00:20:37,920
Once we have the key,

417
00:20:37,960 --> 00:20:39,480
we must quickly disguise its appearance

418
00:20:39,600 --> 00:20:41,240
to become the most common,

419
00:20:41,320 --> 00:20:43,080
most easily overlooked item at the festival.

420
00:20:45,320 --> 00:20:46,080
I understand.

421
00:20:46,960 --> 00:20:49,200
That night, all the female guests will wear hairpins.

422
00:20:49,800 --> 00:20:51,920
We'll turn the key into a hairpin.

423
00:20:52,560 --> 00:20:53,640
I feel that is not safe enough.

424
00:20:54,320 --> 00:20:56,040
If they suspect our identities are fake,

425
00:20:56,240 --> 00:20:57,400
they will definitely search thoroughly.

426
00:20:58,000 --> 00:21:00,200
Each of us, along with Yuan Ran and Wu Qiangu,

427
00:21:00,320 --> 00:21:01,720
must learn how to move the key

428
00:21:01,720 --> 00:21:02,640
quickly among

429
00:21:02,640 --> 00:21:03,840
every female guest at the scene.

430
00:21:04,040 --> 00:21:05,000
As long as, when we finally leave,

431
00:21:05,440 --> 00:21:06,360
it returns to us, that will suffice.

432
00:21:12,760 --> 00:21:13,640
Eunuch Lord Shang.

433
00:21:14,880 --> 00:21:15,400
Your Highness.

434
00:21:15,680 --> 00:21:17,480
Do you think I am here,

435
00:21:17,720 --> 00:21:19,600
over some dispensable item,

436
00:21:20,160 --> 00:21:22,240
troubling the entire court

437
00:21:23,600 --> 00:21:24,520
just to put on a show?

438
00:21:31,840 --> 00:21:32,640
Guards!

439
00:21:33,040 --> 00:21:35,320
Bring Lord Pei Yuandong of the Grand Court of Justice

440
00:21:35,560 --> 00:21:36,200
up here.

441
00:21:42,840 --> 00:21:43,960
Embroidered Uniform Guard Deputy Commander Yin Feng

442
00:21:44,080 --> 00:21:45,240
greets Your Highness.

443
00:21:48,040 --> 00:21:49,240
We received reliable intelligence

444
00:21:49,600 --> 00:21:51,120
that Minister Pei Yuandong of the Grand Court

445
00:21:51,320 --> 00:21:52,800
might be harmed before tonight's lantern festival.

446
00:21:52,920 --> 00:21:54,520
So we rushed to the Grand Court

447
00:21:54,760 --> 00:21:55,560
to investigate.

448
00:21:55,840 --> 00:21:57,840
We happened to save the unconscious Lord Pei.

449
00:22:04,560 --> 00:22:05,480
Commander Shen,

450
00:22:05,800 --> 00:22:06,800
why do you not immediately arrest

451
00:22:06,800 --> 00:22:08,440
this villain posing as Lord Pei?

452
00:22:39,880 --> 00:22:40,880
Master Shen

453
00:22:41,760 --> 00:22:44,400
Which side is your heart on?

454
00:22:46,400 --> 00:22:47,640
Have you thought it through?

455
00:22:47,960 --> 00:22:49,720
You dare bewitch minds at death's door?

456
00:22:50,200 --> 00:22:50,960
Commander Shen

457
00:22:51,200 --> 00:22:52,280
Do I really have to teach you

458
00:22:52,280 --> 00:22:53,360
how to interrogate this villain?

459
00:22:53,440 --> 00:22:54,720
Your subordinate dares not.

460
00:22:57,800 --> 00:22:58,520
Wu Qiangu

461
00:22:59,560 --> 00:23:02,000
Why did you disguise yourself as a high official to enter the palace?

462
00:23:02,480 --> 00:23:02,840
You...

463
00:23:03,840 --> 00:23:05,160
what exactly is your intention?

464
00:23:08,720 --> 00:23:10,360
I heard that tonight,

465
00:23:10,600 --> 00:23:11,560
the Prayer Lantern Festival

466
00:23:11,560 --> 00:23:14,040
is being personally organized by Consort Wan.

467
00:23:14,520 --> 00:23:15,760
I have long wanted to witness

468
00:23:15,760 --> 00:23:17,280
the grace of Her Highness the Consort.

469
00:23:17,920 --> 00:23:18,720
I didn't expect

470
00:23:20,680 --> 00:23:23,320
to run into the palace guards hunting a thief.

471
00:23:30,840 --> 00:23:31,880
The Embroidered Uniform Guard...

472
00:23:32,920 --> 00:23:35,720
when did they become so soft-hearted,

473
00:23:36,320 --> 00:23:37,960
allowing someone to be this arrogant?

474
00:23:38,600 --> 00:23:41,680
Or is it your lack of discipline?

475
00:23:47,840 --> 00:23:48,440
Speak!

476
00:23:49,320 --> 00:23:50,640
Why did you specifically choose

477
00:23:50,640 --> 00:23:51,880
to impersonate Master Pei Yuandong?

478
00:23:56,880 --> 00:23:57,160
Speak!

479
00:23:58,480 --> 00:24:00,160
Why did you specifically choose

480
00:24:00,320 --> 00:24:01,880
to impersonate Master Pei Yuandong?

481
00:24:03,480 --> 00:24:05,600
Among those near me of similar age,

482
00:24:05,920 --> 00:24:07,800
there was only Master Pei.

483
00:24:09,520 --> 00:24:12,480
I actually wanted to copy you, Eunuch Lord Shang,

484
00:24:17,520 --> 00:24:19,560
to copy Eunuch Lord Shang's appearance,

485
00:24:23,040 --> 00:24:24,840
but I'd need the opportunity.

486
00:24:33,600 --> 00:24:35,800
What a loose tongue,

487
00:24:35,960 --> 00:24:37,760
you insubordinate rebel!

488
00:24:39,120 --> 00:24:41,160
If you don't confess who the mastermind is,

489
00:24:41,560 --> 00:24:42,880
I will have you executed immediately

490
00:24:43,120 --> 00:24:44,120
to set an example for all.

491
00:24:54,240 --> 00:24:54,960
Superintendent Wang,

492
00:24:57,920 --> 00:25:00,320
leave such a small matter to me,

493
00:25:00,680 --> 00:25:01,800
so you don't dirty your hands.

494
00:25:02,560 --> 00:25:04,040
Leave it to you?

495
00:25:04,360 --> 00:25:04,960
What?

496
00:25:06,600 --> 00:25:08,040
Do you want to make your Godfather

497
00:25:08,600 --> 00:25:10,120
lose face again?

498
00:25:10,680 --> 00:25:13,120
There is only one chance.

499
00:25:14,000 --> 00:25:16,960
If you can't grasp it, it won't belong to you.

500
00:25:21,800 --> 00:25:23,000
I overstepped my bounds.

501
00:25:25,120 --> 00:25:25,720
Will you speak or not?

502
00:25:25,800 --> 00:25:26,400
Will you speak?

503
00:25:26,920 --> 00:25:27,600
Will you speak?!

504
00:25:30,080 --> 00:25:31,680
Going out now is suicide.

505
00:25:33,920 --> 00:25:35,680
If you get caught in this palace,

506
00:25:36,520 --> 00:25:38,440
the entire Tang Clan will be implicated.

507
00:25:39,640 --> 00:25:42,680
I can't just watch the weird old man...

508
00:25:42,840 --> 00:25:44,480
If you and Zhang Yi jump out now,

509
00:25:44,960 --> 00:25:47,440
everything we've done will fall short.

510
00:25:48,360 --> 00:25:49,600
You will destroy the entire Tang Clan,

511
00:25:50,640 --> 00:25:52,240
and he will destroy the entire Grand Court of Justice.

512
00:26:07,200 --> 00:26:08,360
Eunuch Lord Wang

513
00:26:09,360 --> 00:26:12,280
Although I was saved by the Eastern Depot and Embroidered Uniform Guard,

514
00:26:12,720 --> 00:26:14,160
as the Chief Minister of the Grand Court of Justice,

515
00:26:14,440 --> 00:26:15,640
the laws of the Great Ming...

516
00:26:15,920 --> 00:26:17,640
are still fresh in my mind.

517
00:26:17,680 --> 00:26:19,280
Impersonating a high court official,

518
00:26:19,480 --> 00:26:21,200
claiming office without holding one,

519
00:26:21,200 --> 00:26:22,360
for personal gain,

520
00:26:22,520 --> 00:26:24,200
and assuming an official's name...

521
00:26:24,280 --> 00:26:26,040
One hundred strokes and three years of penal servitude.

522
00:26:26,360 --> 00:26:27,720
Yet you executing someone without authorization...

523
00:26:27,960 --> 00:26:30,080
which article of the Great Ming Law is that based on?

524
00:26:32,520 --> 00:26:35,240
Lord Pei, do you wish to shield this person?

525
00:26:35,680 --> 00:26:38,000
I am merely speaking according to the facts.

526
00:26:38,400 --> 00:26:40,000
I was unconscious when I was rescued.

527
00:26:40,880 --> 00:26:42,400
Everyone knows that.

528
00:26:42,680 --> 00:26:43,200
Very well.

529
00:26:44,480 --> 00:26:45,480
One hundred strokes.

530
00:26:46,920 --> 00:26:48,000
Changed to one hundred lashes.

531
00:26:50,520 --> 00:26:52,480
If Wang Zhi intends to whip Wu Qiangu,

532
00:26:52,600 --> 00:26:53,520
after these one hundred lashes,

533
00:26:53,720 --> 00:26:54,560
death is certain.

534
00:26:56,400 --> 00:26:57,120
Eunuch Lord Wang.

535
00:26:58,000 --> 00:26:59,160
This old man believes...

536
00:26:59,520 --> 00:27:02,640
today is the seventh day since Master Konghui's passing.

537
00:27:02,960 --> 00:27:04,920
Buddhism forbids killing and slaughter.

538
00:27:05,160 --> 00:27:06,240
On a day like this,

539
00:27:06,480 --> 00:27:08,560
to insist on causing a bloodbath...

540
00:27:08,680 --> 00:27:10,040
would affect the nation's fortune in the future,

541
00:27:10,120 --> 00:27:11,520
and no one can bear that responsibility.

542
00:27:11,640 --> 00:27:12,360
Consort Wan.

543
00:27:12,360 --> 00:27:13,880
This absolutely must not happen.

544
00:27:13,960 --> 00:27:15,440
If any misfortune occurs later,

545
00:27:15,760 --> 00:27:17,880
how will Your Highness face His Majesty

546
00:27:18,040 --> 00:27:19,720
and explain today's events?

547
00:27:22,000 --> 00:27:24,560
Please reconsider, Your Highness.

548
00:27:33,080 --> 00:27:33,560
Enough.

549
00:27:34,720 --> 00:27:36,080
The prayer lantern festival will continue.

550
00:27:36,960 --> 00:27:38,480
But thieves have infiltrated the palace,

551
00:27:38,960 --> 00:27:41,000
and this matter involves the Grand Court of Justice.

552
00:27:41,320 --> 00:27:43,680
Detain the families of the Grand Court officials for now,

553
00:27:44,320 --> 00:27:45,840
to prevent further trouble.

554
00:27:55,360 --> 00:27:55,840
Please.

555
00:27:56,000 --> 00:27:56,560
Lord Zhang.

556
00:28:00,840 --> 00:28:02,520
Until the key is found,

557
00:28:03,160 --> 00:28:04,840
no one is allowed to leave.

558
00:28:05,480 --> 00:28:06,320
If there is any suspicious movement,

559
00:28:06,760 --> 00:28:07,760
kill without mercy.

560
00:28:08,040 --> 00:28:09,480
Instead of saying these things,

561
00:28:10,120 --> 00:28:11,600
you'd be better off warning

562
00:28:11,880 --> 00:28:13,960
your godson, who isn't very sharp today.

563
00:28:34,560 --> 00:28:35,520
Drag him away.

564
00:28:45,320 --> 00:28:46,280
Girl.

565
00:28:46,880 --> 00:28:48,360
Run!

566
00:29:04,400 --> 00:29:05,880
I was born free.

567
00:29:07,160 --> 00:29:07,880
And death...

568
00:29:08,920 --> 00:29:11,160
must also be decided by myself.

569
00:29:15,160 --> 00:29:16,560
See you in the martial world.

570
00:29:17,280 --> 00:29:19,120
Or never see you again.

571
00:29:35,960 --> 00:29:37,080
You want to see...

572
00:29:37,440 --> 00:29:38,760
what kind of illusion magic scenery?

573
00:29:39,480 --> 00:29:41,040
Compared to landscapes, flowers, and birds,

574
00:29:42,080 --> 00:29:44,920
I'd rather see the desert scenery of the Western Regions.

575
00:29:47,440 --> 00:29:48,920
But your illusion magic is all fake.

576
00:29:48,920 --> 00:29:50,760
In the end, I have to imagine it myself.

577
00:29:51,600 --> 00:29:52,920
Might as well go see it myself.

578
00:29:53,880 --> 00:29:55,480
Who says my illusion magic is fake?

579
00:29:57,080 --> 00:29:58,680
Falsehood and truth,

580
00:29:58,840 --> 00:30:00,000
real and fake intermingled.

581
00:30:04,400 --> 00:30:05,160
If...

582
00:30:05,880 --> 00:30:07,680
I let you see right here in the capital

583
00:30:07,840 --> 00:30:08,800
the scenery of the great desert,

584
00:30:10,040 --> 00:30:11,240
how do you plan to reward me?

585
00:30:17,040 --> 00:30:17,920
What are you looking at?

586
00:30:18,960 --> 00:30:21,040
The night before last was a mistake.

587
00:30:22,800 --> 00:30:24,000
A beautiful mistake.

588
00:30:30,680 --> 00:30:31,640
What do you want?

589
00:30:33,640 --> 00:30:34,600
What do I want?

590
00:30:36,720 --> 00:30:37,560
I want...

591
00:30:37,960 --> 00:30:39,760
you all to embrace the freedom of this world,

592
00:30:40,240 --> 00:30:40,920
feel love,

593
00:30:41,360 --> 00:30:42,760
and enjoy the life of ordinary people.

594
00:30:43,560 --> 00:30:45,480
My brother-in-law told me these words.

595
00:30:45,800 --> 00:30:46,360
And then?

596
00:30:47,000 --> 00:30:47,720
He died.

597
00:31:21,440 --> 00:31:22,680
It seems everything went smoothly.

598
00:31:57,840 --> 00:31:58,400
Your Highness.

599
00:32:22,800 --> 00:32:23,160
Let's go.

600
00:32:50,560 --> 00:32:51,240
Who are you?

601
00:32:51,960 --> 00:32:53,000
I am Wan Zhen'er.

602
00:32:53,480 --> 00:32:54,040
Nonsense.

603
00:32:54,720 --> 00:32:56,240
How dare you impersonate me?

604
00:32:56,920 --> 00:32:58,200
In the entire Ming Dynasty,

605
00:32:58,200 --> 00:32:59,160
no one would dare do such a thing.

606
00:33:01,960 --> 00:33:03,000
Look at you now,

607
00:33:03,000 --> 00:33:04,400
looking like neither human nor ghost.

608
00:33:04,560 --> 00:33:06,640
How are you worthy of the name Wan Zhen'er?

609
00:33:07,840 --> 00:33:08,840
Your virtue does not match your status.

610
00:33:09,360 --> 00:33:10,320
Disaster will surely follow.

611
00:33:10,440 --> 00:33:11,120
Insolence!

612
00:33:11,920 --> 00:33:12,840
You lowly maid!

613
00:33:13,240 --> 00:33:14,680
How dare you slander me like this!

614
00:33:15,040 --> 00:33:16,320
Though I started as a palace maid,

615
00:33:16,800 --> 00:33:17,920
I have served since childhood

616
00:33:17,920 --> 00:33:19,240
by the side of Empress Dowager Sun.

617
00:33:19,520 --> 00:33:21,800
At nineteen, I cared for His Majesty when he was two.

618
00:33:22,160 --> 00:33:24,080
I shared the wealth when he was Crown Prince,

619
00:33:24,480 --> 00:33:25,720
and I endured with him

620
00:33:25,720 --> 00:33:27,200
the hardships when he was demoted to Prince of Yi.

621
00:33:27,960 --> 00:33:28,720
He respects me,

622
00:33:29,080 --> 00:33:29,920
pities me,

623
00:33:30,240 --> 00:33:30,680
and protects me.

624
00:33:31,240 --> 00:33:32,800
Have I not treated him the same?

625
00:33:33,400 --> 00:33:34,040
But you,

626
00:33:34,600 --> 00:33:36,160
blinded by the lust for power,

627
00:33:36,640 --> 00:33:38,520
plotted to let villains take his life,

628
00:33:38,520 --> 00:33:39,080
harm his empire,

629
00:33:39,080 --> 00:33:39,880
and harm his heirs.

630
00:33:40,200 --> 00:33:41,640
Can you face His Majesty after that?

631
00:33:46,960 --> 00:33:47,720
Consort Wan!

632
00:33:47,960 --> 00:33:49,040
Cover your mouth and nose, quickly!

633
00:33:49,320 --> 00:33:50,800
Be careful not to inhale the Illusion Magic potion.

634
00:33:52,360 --> 00:33:53,080
Consort Wan!

635
00:34:16,200 --> 00:34:16,880
Wang Zhi!

636
00:34:17,320 --> 00:34:17,800
Tell me,

637
00:34:18,280 --> 00:34:20,040
did you do all of this today?

638
00:34:20,320 --> 00:34:21,400
Why was there an explosion?

639
00:34:22,440 --> 00:34:24,480
You organized this lantern festival single-handedly.

640
00:34:24,920 --> 00:34:27,160
I never authorized the Western Depot to buy saltpeter.

641
00:34:28,000 --> 00:34:29,160
Where did this saltpeter come from?

642
00:34:30,120 --> 00:34:30,800
Your Highness,

643
00:34:31,160 --> 00:34:32,240
this has nothing to do with me.

644
00:34:32,480 --> 00:34:34,600
Do not trust that sorcerer's nonsense.

645
00:34:35,080 --> 00:34:36,240
Seize Wang Zhi!

646
00:34:37,000 --> 00:34:37,960
Your Highness!

647
00:34:39,880 --> 00:34:40,400
Superintendent Wang,

648
00:34:40,400 --> 00:34:40,960
forgive me.

649
00:34:41,680 --> 00:34:43,640
After all, this is Consort Wan's order.

650
00:34:44,920 --> 00:34:45,880
I believe His Majesty

651
00:34:46,040 --> 00:34:47,240
will soon arrive with the Imperial Guard

652
00:34:47,240 --> 00:34:48,040
and the Embroidered Uniform Guard.

653
00:34:49,320 --> 00:34:50,280
Everyone, stay calm.

654
00:34:50,960 --> 00:34:51,720
Zhang Yi,

655
00:34:52,240 --> 00:34:53,760
they have already escaped.

656
00:34:54,960 --> 00:34:55,800
Commander Shen,

657
00:34:56,640 --> 00:34:59,120
go catch the escaped criminals at once!

658
00:34:59,840 --> 00:35:00,520
Commander Yuan,

659
00:35:01,080 --> 00:35:02,480
follow me out of the city to arrest Tang Xi and the others.

660
00:35:02,800 --> 00:35:03,160
Yes, sir.

661
00:35:18,480 --> 00:35:19,960
It looks like we're going to die here today.

662
00:35:21,080 --> 00:35:21,680
Tang Xi,

663
00:35:22,240 --> 00:35:23,080
your martial arts are the best.

664
00:35:23,480 --> 00:35:24,360
If there is a chance,

665
00:35:24,520 --> 00:35:25,160
Don't worry.

666
00:35:26,160 --> 00:35:26,960
You'll live longer than me.

667
00:35:27,240 --> 00:35:28,120
They have us outnumbered.

668
00:35:28,440 --> 00:35:29,160
We cannot fight for long.

669
00:35:29,840 --> 00:35:30,840
Find a way to open the palace gates

670
00:35:31,320 --> 00:35:32,280
and regroup with Lu Shijie.

671
00:35:32,560 --> 00:35:33,640
You handle Shen Youzhi and his men.

672
00:35:33,920 --> 00:35:35,080
Beauty, you handle those ninjas.

673
00:35:35,480 --> 00:35:36,280
I'll go open the palace gates.

674
00:35:36,480 --> 00:35:37,360
Once the gates are open,

675
00:35:37,640 --> 00:35:38,600
focus on escaping.

676
00:35:38,800 --> 00:35:39,360
Do not linger in battle.

677
00:35:39,520 --> 00:35:39,840
Okay.

678
00:35:40,040 --> 00:35:40,680
Split up!

679
00:36:14,120 --> 00:36:16,360
I am Fujii Musashi, the greatest swordsman of the East

680
00:36:16,720 --> 00:36:18,000
Today, commissioned by the Western Depot

681
00:36:18,200 --> 00:36:19,320
I come to take your heads

682
00:36:19,760 --> 00:36:20,440
What a coincidence

683
00:36:20,600 --> 00:36:22,400
The last person who dared call himself the greatest swordsman

684
00:36:22,560 --> 00:36:24,200
...was buried just a few days ago

685
00:36:24,720 --> 00:36:26,240
Even Japanese pirates must follow local customs

686
00:36:32,200 --> 00:36:33,080
Vice Minister Zhang

687
00:36:33,680 --> 00:36:34,800
Just now, Wu Qiangu

688
00:36:35,280 --> 00:36:36,720
...was executed on the spot

689
00:36:37,840 --> 00:36:39,240
You were coerced by bandits

690
00:36:40,000 --> 00:36:41,480
...to flee to the palace gates

691
00:36:42,800 --> 00:36:44,320
You need not worry anymore

692
00:36:46,240 --> 00:36:47,480
Who said I was coerced?

693
00:36:47,640 --> 00:36:48,320
Zhang Yi

694
00:36:53,160 --> 00:36:54,640
It's not too late to turn back now

695
00:36:55,800 --> 00:36:57,320
Hand over what you took

696
00:36:57,320 --> 00:36:58,640
Or no one leaves here today

697
00:36:59,200 --> 00:36:59,960
You must know

698
00:37:01,160 --> 00:37:02,480
...you are different from them

699
00:37:03,720 --> 00:37:04,760
How am I different?

700
00:37:05,480 --> 00:37:06,920
We are all doing the same thing

701
00:37:18,480 --> 00:37:19,000
Here's a blade for you

702
00:37:23,120 --> 00:37:24,640
For the sake of us once serving as officials together

703
00:37:25,640 --> 00:37:26,640
...show some mercy

704
00:39:08,200 --> 00:39:08,840
Stop chasing

705
00:39:12,240 --> 00:39:12,720
Go

706
00:39:37,960 --> 00:39:38,520
It's useless

707
00:39:38,840 --> 00:39:40,040
You shouldn't have come in tonight

708
00:39:41,000 --> 00:39:41,760
I felt like it

709
00:40:12,680 --> 00:40:13,960
Is it worth risking your lives like this?

710
00:40:16,440 --> 00:40:17,600
At such a young age

711
00:40:17,640 --> 00:40:19,560
...you've learned to hesitate before even fighting

712
00:40:21,240 --> 00:40:22,400
To die without fighting

713
00:40:22,600 --> 00:40:23,600
...is so boring

714
00:40:24,840 --> 00:40:26,160
Only by keeping on fighting

715
00:40:26,360 --> 00:40:27,320
...can one avoid defeat

716
00:40:29,040 --> 00:40:30,000
Even if I die

717
00:40:30,360 --> 00:40:31,080
...I won't regret it

718
00:40:59,960 --> 00:41:00,600
How are you doing?

719
00:41:01,040 --> 00:41:01,880
Cut the crap

720
00:41:03,520 --> 00:41:04,760
Qian Ben is here to help us

721
00:41:08,320 --> 00:41:09,440
You two hold him off first

722
00:41:10,160 --> 00:41:11,000
We'll go open the palace gates

723
00:41:12,240 --> 00:41:12,680
Okay

724
00:41:28,640 --> 00:41:29,400
Go help them, quick

725
00:41:29,520 --> 00:41:30,280
Leave this to me

726
00:41:36,200 --> 00:41:37,080
Qian Ben

727
00:41:37,960 --> 00:41:38,680
Why?

728
00:41:51,200 --> 00:41:51,960
Qian Ben!

729
00:41:56,600 --> 00:41:57,240
Qian Ben!

730
00:42:06,920 --> 00:42:07,800
Tang Xi, catch this

731
00:42:34,360 --> 00:42:35,080
Qian Ben!

732
00:42:35,720 --> 00:42:36,320
Why?

733
00:42:36,800 --> 00:42:37,840
Why did you do this?

734
00:42:53,480 --> 00:42:54,080
Qian Ben!

735
00:42:55,560 --> 00:42:56,240
Qian Ben!

736
00:43:21,080 --> 00:43:21,840
Today

737
00:43:22,600 --> 00:43:23,680
...the rules of the martial world

738
00:43:24,800 --> 00:43:26,080
...repay kindness with kindness

739
00:43:26,960 --> 00:43:28,320
...and hatred with vengeance

740
00:43:28,640 --> 00:43:29,720
It doesn't end until death

741
00:43:31,520 --> 00:43:32,080
Enough!

742
00:43:33,600 --> 00:43:35,160
Let's see who dares take a step forward!

743
00:43:37,440 --> 00:43:38,760
In my imperial palace

744
00:43:40,480 --> 00:43:41,880
...Japanese ninjas have appeared

745
00:43:42,400 --> 00:43:43,520
Anyone who does not kill the foreign enemy

746
00:43:44,480 --> 00:43:46,240
...but kills my Ming children instead

747
00:43:46,680 --> 00:43:47,840
...shall be deemed a traitor

748
00:43:49,000 --> 00:43:50,240
Kill without mercy!

749
00:43:55,040 --> 00:43:55,960
Shen Youzhi!

750
00:43:56,600 --> 00:43:58,520
Even at the end, you are cowardly

751
00:43:59,600 --> 00:44:00,760
What is the point of living?

752
00:44:04,760 --> 00:44:06,040
Everyone, listen to my order!

753
00:44:07,320 --> 00:44:08,400
Everyone, listen to my order!

754
00:44:10,000 --> 00:44:11,120
When we arrived

755
00:44:11,600 --> 00:44:13,320
...Tang Xi and the others had already killed the Japanese thieves

756
00:44:13,320 --> 00:44:14,360
...and escaped through the palace gate

757
00:44:14,400 --> 00:44:15,600
Is that clear?

758
00:44:23,560 --> 00:44:24,360
Why aren't you leaving yet?

759
00:44:26,120 --> 00:44:27,120
Don't come back

760
00:44:32,480 --> 00:44:33,000
Go

761
00:44:58,960 --> 00:45:00,160
Where are Zhang Yi and Tang Xi?

762
00:45:06,640 --> 00:45:07,920
Womanly benevolence

763
00:45:19,920 --> 00:45:21,200
Superfluous emotions

764
00:45:21,640 --> 00:45:22,480
...will all become

765
00:45:22,480 --> 00:45:24,120
...stumbling blocks on your path to the peak of power

766
00:45:25,160 --> 00:45:25,600
I...

767
00:45:26,800 --> 00:45:29,760
...when have I ever disappointed you?

768
00:45:57,400 --> 00:45:58,080
Quick, quick, quick!

769
00:45:58,160 --> 00:45:58,520
Move it!

770
00:45:58,600 --> 00:45:58,960
Quick!

771
00:45:59,040 --> 00:45:59,400
Quick!

772
00:45:59,680 --> 00:46:00,040
Quick!

773
00:46:00,520 --> 00:46:00,880
Yuan Ran

774
00:46:02,280 --> 00:46:03,080
Why are there only three of you?

775
00:46:03,360 --> 00:46:03,920
Where is Old Wu?
